This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the moonshotai organization:
- moonshotai/Kimi-K2-Instruct tokenizer snapshot
- moonshotai/Kimi-K2-Thinking tokenizer snapshot
- moonshotai/Moonlight-16B-A3B tokenizer snapshot
- moonshotai/Kimi-Dev-72B tokenizer snapshot

The following supported model names are aliases confirmed to reuse those bundled tokenizer assets and are not shipped as separate snapshots:
- moonshotai/Kimi-K2-Base
- moonshotai/Kimi-K2-Instruct-0905
- moonshotai/Kimi-Linear-48B-A3B-Base
- moonshotai/Kimi-Linear-48B-A3B-Instruct
- moonshotai/Moonlight-16B-A3B-Instruct

See LICENSE and NOTICE for the full license text and attribution notices that
apply to this package and its bundled assets.
